South Georgia Tormenta FC Logo South Georgia Tormenta FC is an American soccer organization based in Statesboro, Georgia, United States. Founded in 2015, the club fields a professional team in USL League One, the third tier of the American Soccer Pyramid, as well as a pre-professional team in USL League Two called Tormenta FC 2. The team colors are midnight navy, sky blue, silver, and magenta. The team’s crest shows an ibis. Source
